            ApplyLowHpHeroAttackSafety(board, p, enemyHp, enemyAttackSnapshot);

            // 鐢ㄦ埛瑙勫垯锛氶殢鑸瑰绉戝尰甯堬紙CORE_WON_065锛夊繀椤讳紭鍏堣В銆?
